cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NI 

The paper focuses on developing an authentication framework for IoT objects, which is a critical aspect of IoT security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also uses transfer learning and environmental effects estimation to improve the authentication accuracy, which falls under the categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The proposed framework also considers the physical environment, which is related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
